  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Board the Rocky Mountaineer and explore Canada one of the most iconic routes through the Rocky Mountains. Passing dramatically-changing countryside while travelling through valleys, canyons and mountain passes. End your trip in the remote and untamed wilderness of the Yukon and explore</span><span> rugged trails, shorelines and forests and hope to witness the dazzling blue, green and red spectacle of the Northern Lights.</span></p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/mountain-rails-northern-lights-adventure#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/mountain-rails-northern-lights-adventure#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/mountain-rails-northern-lights-adventure#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/mountain-rails-northern-lights-adventure#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-canada/mountain-rails-northern-lights-adventure#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
