<p><strong>★★★  Thompson Hotel, Kamloops (1 night)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ Georgian Court Hotel OR Coast Coal Harbour Vancouver Hotel by APA, Vancouver (3 nights)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★  Southern Lakes Resort, Tagish (3 nights)</strong></p>
<p> </p>
