<p><strong>★★★★ Fairmont Banff Springs Hotel or Rimrock Resort Hotel, Banff (2 nights) </strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge or Sawridge Inn &amp; Conference Centre, Jasper (2 nights)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★  Thompson Hotel, Kamloops (1 night)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ Fairmont Hotel Vancouver or ★★★★★ Pan Pacific Hotel Vancouver, Vancouver (3 nights)</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★  Southern Lakes Resort, Tagish (3 nights)</strong></p>
<p><em>If one of the listed hotels is not available, it will be replaced with alternate accommodation of a similar quality.</em></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>GoldLeaf Upgrade</strong></p>
<p>For travelers seeking ultimate luxury and upgraded service on board the Rocky Mountaineer, the special GoldLeaf Service is available. Featuring a fully glass-domed cabin offering the best and most magnificent views and a separate dining car that offers fine dining. Upgrade at time of booking to ensure availability.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a name="Departure dates"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Departure dates<a></a></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Wednesday and Saturday departures from 15 August-30 September</li>
</ul>
